high_descs: Turn to your right to look at the trashcan
Pick up the bottle inside of the trashcan
Step to your left, and then continue down to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the bottle on the bottom of shelf, close it, then open it back up and pick up the bottle
Turn to your right, then go back over to the trashcan in the left corner of the room
Put the bottle back into the trashcan
anns.task_desc: Pick up a bottle, place it into the fridge, take it back to the trash

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the wall then turn left and move to the garbage bin next to the counter.
Pick up the bottle of wine from the garbage bin.
Turn left, move towards the table in the corner, then turn right and move past the sink to reach the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the bottle of wine on the bottom shelf to the left of the egg, chill the wine, then open the refrigerator, pick up the bottle of wine, and close the refrigerator door.
Turn right, move past the sink, then turn left and move to the silver garbage bin next to the counter.
Place the bottle of wine into the garbage bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bottle of wine into the garbage bin.

high_descs: Turn to the right, and locate the trash can on the left.
Pick up the bottle from inside the trash can.
Take the bottle and go left to find the fridge on the far right side.
Open the fridge and place the bottle inside on the bottom shelf and shut the door. Open the fridge, and take out the bottle.
Go across the room to the right, and back to the trash can to the left and the end of the counter.
Place the bottle back in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Move the bottle from and back to the trash can.
